OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain will mostly clear away
OL,6,Fthrough the morning, although staying
OL,7,Fquite cloudy with some light rain
OL,8,Flingering into the afternoon, mainly
OL,9,Fover the southwest. Further rain
OL,10,Fspreads into the southwest in the late
OL,11,Fafternoon. Warm.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain spreads north through
OL,14,Fthe evening. This clearing before
OL,15,Fmidnight to leave a largely dry night
OL,16,Fwith some clear spells developing.
OL,17,FMore cloud and rain into the southwest
OL,18,Fby morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
