OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FWarm again. A quite cloudy
OL,6,Fmorning with patchy drizzle in the
OL,7,Fwest. Dry afternoon with bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWarm
OL,11,Fover the weekend and on Monday with
OL,12,Fmostly bright or sunny spells, but
OL,13,Fgenerally cloudier in the southwest.
OL,14,Fchance of some rain later on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
